  "detailed_description": "'Tally-ho, kids!<br>Are you ready for another carrot'd adventure? <br>Starring your 3rd favourite cartoon carrot?!'<br><br>Join Captain Carrot as he returns to the call of adventure throughout the Vegetable Kingdom!<br><br>Grab your bowl of Captain Carrot cereal and a tall glass of tomato-orange juice and join our hero Captain Carrot as he returns to his Saturday morning adventures through the Vegetable Kingdom!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/4efe4735d9c1e5932037928efded47e5.poster.avif?t=1680627630\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/4efe4735d9c1e5932037928efded47e5.webm?t=1680627630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/4efe4735d9c1e5932037928efded47e5.mp4?t=1680627630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>YOU SHALL! Encounter a cornucopia of baddies, obstacles, new forms, and platforming challenges as you traverse the various stages!<br><br>THIS GAME IS! A challenging 2D platformer with an emphasis on movement, ground pound timing, and a falling double jump called a 'carrot jump' inspired by classic Saturday cartoons.<br><br>IT FEATURES! <br>- an overworld to roam!<br>- unlock new forms with new play styles!<br>- colourful enemies to best and NPCs to meet!<br>- a slay spare boss system!<br>- multiple endings!<br>- bird watching<br>- shops and items to unlock different areas!<br>- fishing, surfing.... and volleyball?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/eecde2ba1978ad1191aeb637f3660f1b.poster.avif?t=1680627630\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/eecde2ba1978ad1191aeb637f3660f1b.webm?t=1680627630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/eecde2ba1978ad1191aeb637f3660f1b.mp4?t=1680627630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
  "about_the_game": "'Tally-ho, kids!<br>Are you ready for another carrot'd adventure? <br>Starring your 3rd favourite cartoon carrot?!'<br><br>Join Captain Carrot as he returns to the call of adventure throughout the Vegetable Kingdom!<br><br>Grab your bowl of Captain Carrot cereal and a tall glass of tomato-orange juice and join our hero Captain Carrot as he returns to his Saturday morning adventures through the Vegetable Kingdom!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/4efe4735d9c1e5932037928efded47e5.poster.avif?t=1680627630\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/4efe4735d9c1e5932037928efded47e5.webm?t=1680627630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/4efe4735d9c1e5932037928efded47e5.mp4?t=1680627630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>YOU SHALL! Encounter a cornucopia of baddies, obstacles, new forms, and platforming challenges as you traverse the various stages!<br><br>THIS GAME IS! A challenging 2D platformer with an emphasis on movement, ground pound timing, and a falling double jump called a 'carrot jump' inspired by classic Saturday cartoons.<br><br>IT FEATURES! <br>- an overworld to roam!<br>- unlock new forms with new play styles!<br>- colourful enemies to best and NPCs to meet!<br>- a slay spare boss system!<br>- multiple endings!<br>- bird watching<br>- shops and items to unlock different areas!<br>- fishing, surfing.... and volleyball?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1632530/extras/eecde2ba1978ad1191aeb637f3660f1b.poster.avif?t=1680627630\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.ak